NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|I have used this approach quite successfully for many years. I am not sure why more people don't play it. In this example, Anna has a borderline hand. Its not clear whether or not she has a game force. Personally, with 2 aces, I would call her hand a game force and she can bid 2@H (4th Suit).|
